@startuml child_lock_and_access_auth_to_door_rl_unlock_gate_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Child Lock And Access Auth To Door RL Unlock Gate Signal Flow\n(door control + child-lock + access authorization -> DOOR_RL unlock gate)

participant "Door-control bus" as DoorCtl #F4F7FB
participant "Vehicle state bus" as Veh #E8F0FE
participant "Digital-key /\nimmobilizer buses" as Access #FCE8FF
participant "DOOR_RL\nrear-left door owner" as DoorRL #E8F7E8
participant "Door RL state bus" as DoorBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nbody readers" as Obs #FFF4CC

== Door RL Inputs ==

DoorCtl -> DoorRL : frmDoorControlMsg\nDoorControlCmd / ChildLockCmd
Veh -> DoorRL : frmVehicleStateCanMsg\ngDriveState
Access -> DoorRL : frmDigitalKeyStateMsg\nVehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
Access -> DoorRL : frmImmobilizerStateMsg\nImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
activate DoorRL
DoorRL -> DoorRL : freshness checks for\ndoor control, vehicle, dkey, immo
DoorRL -> DoorRL : manualMode may read\nChassis::driveState directly
DoorRL -> DoorRL : accessAuthorized =\nparked vehicle and dkey/immo auth valid
DoorRL -> DoorRL : unlockRequest =\nDoorControlCmd > 0
DoorRL -> DoorRL : childLockActive =\nChildLockCmd > 0
DoorRL -> DoorRL : unlock only when\nauthorized and requested and child-lock == 0
note right of DoorRL
Representative gating inputs
- DoorControlCmd
- ChildLockCmd
- gDriveState
- VehicleAccessState / KeyPresence
- ImmobilizerState / KeyAuthState
end note

== Door RL Publish ==

DoorRL -> DoorBus : frmDoorRlStateMsg\nDoorRlLockState / DoorRlOpenState / DoorRlWindowPos
note right of DoorRL
Representative outputs
- DoorRlLockState
- DoorRlOpenState
- DoorRlWindowPos
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

DoorBus -> Obs : rear-left door lock visibility /\nbody observers
deactivate DoorRL

note over DoorCtl, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Door control, vehicle, digital-key, and immobilizer context reach DOOR_RL
2. DOOR_RL resolves access authorization and child-lock posture
3. Unlock request is gated by park state and child-lock release
4. DOOR_RL publishes final rear-left door lock state
end note

@enduml
